data.description: Ranch home with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and over 1,400 square feet of finished space. The main floor offers a living room with wood burning fireplace, kitchen, separate dining area, three bedrooms with hardwood floors, full bathroom, and a three season porch with over 130 square feet. The lower level offers a family room/rec room with a bar, wood burning fireplace, and an additional bathroom. Concrete driveway leads to a two car garage. Large city lot, .31 acres. Vinyl siding and vinyl windows throughout.
